### Variables
@productId = 7f77531f-6f65-444d-92a4-17761176efe1

### Create Product Review
# Note: Run auth.http login/register first to set the token variable
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "rating": 5,
  "title": "Great product!",
  "body": "Very pleased with the purchase. Top quality, fast delivery. I recommend!"
}

### Create Product Review (Negative)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "rating": 2,
  "title": "Didn't live up to expectations",
  "body": "The quality of the product leaves much to be desired. Doesn't match the description."
}

### Get Product Reviews by Product ID (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product-review/by-product/{{productId}}?page=1&page_size=10&sort_by_rating=desc
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Product Reviews by Product ID (without pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product-review/by-product/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Product Reviews by Product ID (page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product-review/by-product/{{productId}}?page=2&page_size=20
Content-Type: application/json
